title: Joey Pickens wins 27th Dewey Beach Sprint Triathlon | Cape Gazette
text: Joey Pickens of Clarksville, Md., smashed the field at the 2024 Dewey Beach Sprint Triathlon Sept. 14, posting a time of 1:17:41 to win by nearly four minutes over second-place finisher Bryan Christ. Amanda Carter of Pinehurst, N.C., was the top female finisher, crossing the line 12th overall in a time of 1:28:25. Second place went to Liz Kligensmith of Lewes with a time of 1:30:13. Full results can be found at [trisignup.com/Race/Results/70303#resultSetId-486832](https://www.trisignup.com/Race/Results/70303#resultSetId-486832).
